{"source_id":"W402","platform":"RSS","author":"AUTOMATON RSS","account_type":"メディア","text":"マルチ対応過酷サバイバル『Don’t Starve Together』リリース10周年で「Steam同接12万人」、歴代最高記録更新。“148円セール”はまだ間に合う\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://automaton-media.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/20260622-451002-header.jpg\" width=\"1600\" /></p>デベロッパーのKlei Entertainmentが手がけるマルチプレイ対応サバイバルゲーム『Don’t Starve Together』の同時接続プレイヤー数が12万2662を記録した。","url":"https://automaton-media.com/articles/newsjp/20260622-451002/","timestamp":"2026-06-22T04:44:57Z","extra":{"source_priority":"high","source_genre":"games","source_type":"メディア"}}
